                "Activities": "<section>\n<h2>Activities</h2>\n<h3>Financial Operations</h3>\n<ul>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Invoicing Verification</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">To verify if a customer, partner, or client has been invoiced, please provide the relevant client details, contract number, or Sales Force link. Contact: Sivakumar Govindan (Finance Operations). System: Sales Force.</span>\n<a itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https://eslfaceitgroup.lightning.force.com/lightning/page/home\">Sales Force</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Prize Money Payments</h3>\n<p>EFG utilizes Payment Labs Inc. for B2C and B2B prize money payouts for all payments from 1 January 2026 onwards. The process involves:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tournament operations set up the tournament on the platform.</li>\n<li>Tournament operations request the funding of the prize money.</li>\n<li>Financial operations process the funding to the For Benefit Of (FBO) account on the platform.</li>\n<li>Tournament operations request winners' payment details and set up payments on the platform.</li>\n<li>Payment Labs collects and stores banking details from winners.</li>\n<li>The 'Payment Approval Group' submits the payment to the winners.</li>\n<li>Financial operations perform monthly reconciliation of platform transactions and prize money payouts.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Procurement</h3>\n<ul>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Procurement and Sourcing</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">Managed by Charlotte Friant (Senior Procurement Manager). Responsibilities include leading the full sourcing lifecycle (RFx process, bid analysis, negotiation), supplier and risk management, and providing procurement support for EWC, ENC, Broadcast commodities, and PC&amp;S topics.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Financial Controlling and FP&amp;A</h3>\n<ul>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Financial Planning and Analysis</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">Led by Matt Simpson (VP FP&amp;A and Controlling). Responsibilities include delivering the 5-year plan, budget, in-year re-forecasts, and monthly reporting.</span>\n</li>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Project Financial Support</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">Business Unit Controllers (e.g., Youssef EL Margou, Jalal Tantaoui) support financial planning, track project performance against budgets, and provide financial insights for Esports business units.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Tax and Treasury</h3>\n<ul>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Tax Compliance</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">Managed by Gergely Jambor (Global Tax Manager). Responsibilities include tax compliance, transfer pricing documentation, and advising on tax terms during contract negotiations.</span>\n</li>\n<li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Service\">\n<strong itemprop=\"name\">Treasury Management</strong>\n<span itemprop=\"description\">Managed by Georg Schmadl (Head of Treasury). Responsibilities include managing banking structures, liquidity, cash flow forecasting, foreign exchange trading, and corporate credit card policy.</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
                "Calendar": "<section>\n  <h2>Finance Division Meeting and Calendar Structure</h2>\n  <p>The Finance division operates under a structured meeting cadence designed to ensure strategic alignment, operational visibility, and effective team management. Specific dates and times for these meetings are maintained in the linked external calendar.</p>\n\n  <h3>Recurring Cadences</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Finance Townhall</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Quarterly cadence. A department-wide session for company announcements, guest speakers, and individual/team achievements.</span>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Leadership Pulse</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Monthly cadence. Focused on strategic alignment, escalation handling, and cascading information down to teams. Participants include L1-3 leadership.</span>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Initiative Sync</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Monthly cadence. An operational meeting for L3 and below to provide visibility on project progress (using the Jira board) and highlight \"wins\".</span>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">Functional Tactical</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Team-dependent cadence. Team-specific meetings led by Matt, Bassem, and Markus to align on day-to-day priorities, unblock tasks, and manage workload. Frequency is determined by the department lead.</span>\n    </li>\n    <li itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Event\">\n      <strong itemprop=\"name\">1:1s: Managers</strong>\n      <span itemprop=\"description\">Weekly cadence. Managers are required to maintain weekly 1:1 meetings with their direct reports.</span>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Sourcing Business Partner Meetings</h3>\n  <p>In addition to the core department cadences, specific procurement meetings are held for business partners:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Publisher Operations:</strong> Wednesdays, 3:30 PM GMT</li>\n    <li><strong>EWC/ENC:</strong> Wednesdays, 09:00 PM GMT</li>\n    <li><strong>O&O:</strong> Wednesdays, 10:00 AM GMT</li>\n    <li><strong>MENA Operations:</strong> Thursdays, 10:00 AM GMT</li>\n    <li><strong>Enterprise Technology:</strong> Tuesdays, 01:30 PM GMT</li>\n    <li><strong>Other Enabling Functions:</strong> As required</li>\n    <li><strong>HR:</strong> As required</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
                "Departments": "<section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n  <h2>Finance Division Departments</h2>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Accounting, Tax & Treasury</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Bassem Masrouha</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">SVP Accounting, Tax and Treasury</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Germany, Duesseldorf</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Stefan Beitz. Responsibilities: Develop, implement, and enforce policies and procedures; direct accounting and tax functions; manage financial accounting systems, internal controls, and external audits; review customer contracts; prepare financial statements; manage cash and foreign exchange.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Gergely Jambor</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Global Tax Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Austria, Vienna</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Masrouha. Responsibilities: Tax compliance; determine Lead Entity allocation; review tax terms in contracts; advise on entity selection; manage transfer pricing; support accounting with KSA WHT review; tax planning; coordinate audits.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Georg Schmadl</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Head of Treasury</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Spain, Barcelona</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Masrouha. Responsibilities: Manage banking structure, liquidity, and cash flow forecasting; treasury reporting; foreign exchange trading; approve payments; credit card management; manage working capital; bank KYC.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Financial Controlling</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">André Bernardino</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Finance Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Portugal, Lisbon</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Matt Simpson. Responsibilities: Managing financial controllers for Esports and Digital; month-end and year-end closing tasks; reviewing Salesforce revenue opportunities; approving POs; cost analysis, budgeting, and forecasting.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Sara Salwey</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Sweden, Stockholm</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Andre Bernardino. Responsibilities: Analyze and manage COGS for Counter Strike (CS) and DOTA; assist project managers with financial queries.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Youssef EL Margou</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Business Unit Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Bulgaria, Budapest</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Jalal Tantaoui. Responsibilities: Support financial planning, analysis, and reporting for Esports projects; prepare budgets and rolling forecasts; track project performance; support cost control; prepare financial reports; build automated financial tools.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Jalal Tantaoui</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Business Unit Controller - MENA</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Germany, Cologne</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Kevin Colvin. Responsibilities: Primary contact for EWC/ENC in Controlling; collaborate with Esports World Cup Foundation; monitor Master Budget Files; approve POs and invoices; SAP COGS data validation; review SOWs.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Ruben Hoskens</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Spain, Barcelona</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: André Bernardino. Responsibilities: Control project actuals against budget and forecasts; verify accuracy of project financial data; partner with project managers to close projects; report standardized financial data.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Corporate Controlling</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Mohammed Sohel Siddique</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">UK, London</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Andre Bernardino. Responsibilities: Manage SG&A accruals and deferrals, UK office VAT, Face It points data, ESL Shop, HR accruals, open POs review, and software capitalization.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Tasso Kouklas</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">FP&A and Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Germany, Cologne</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Alex van Ryswyck. Responsibilities: Allocate costs; explain overspending; verify PO requisitions; manage budgets and forecasts.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Imran Mohammed</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior FPA & Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">UK</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Alexandra van Ryswyck. Responsibilities: Control non-personnel opex; finance business partner for Group Management, Finance, Technology, and Digital Platform; manage monthly reporting, budgeting, forecasting, and PO approvals.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Marcin Spłocharski</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior FP&A and Financial Controller</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Poland</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Alexandra van Ryswyck. Responsibilities: Month-end tasks; headcount and FTE reporting; HR accruals; personnel OPEX control and analysis; budgeting and forecasting; model FTE and personnel costs; finance business partner for PC&S and Legal; drive improvements in people costs processes.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">FP&A</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Matt Simpson</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">VP FP&A and Controlling</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">UK, London</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Stefan Beitz. Responsibilities: Lead FP&A and Controlling team; deliver 5-year plan, budget, re-forecasts, and monthly reporting; ensure accuracy of financial bookings; partner with business on project codes and cost centre financials; provide financial insights and analysis.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Salih Nas</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">FP&A Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Germany, Berlin</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Kevin Colvin. Responsibilities: Manage 'GM2' calculations and hours watched KPI collection; prepare esports 5-year planning; support corporate controlling with capex planning.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Deborah Frost</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior FP&A Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">UK, London</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Matt Simpson. Responsibilities: Managing Digital Platform KPIs; managing month-end and year-end closing tasks related to Digital product; preparing budget, forecast, long-range plan, and financial models.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Kevin Colvin</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Director FP&A</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">USA, Columbus</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Matt Simpson. Responsibilities: Lead FP&A; own planning cycles; partner with commercial/game partnerships; support contract structuring; analyze revenue, COGS, Labor, CM2, and FX; build bridge analyses; improve forecast governance; shape project codes; design and automate finance processes.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Financial Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Alexander Södergren</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Group Financial Accountant</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Sweden, Stockholm</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Julia Rausch. Responsibilities: Month and year-end closing tasks; statutory reporting including VAT & pension for EFG Sweden AB; statutory audit for Sweden and Denmark.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Jason Muno</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Group Financial Accountant</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">USA, New York</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Julia Rausch. Responsibilities: Month and year-end closing tasks; statutory reporting for US entities.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Julia Rausch</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Corporate Accountant</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Germany, Aachen</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Masrouha. Responsibilities: Managing consolidation and group financial reporting; ensuring accuracy, compliance, and timely Group reporting.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Awais Mohammad</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Group Financial Accountant</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">UK, London</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Julia Rausch. Responsibilities: Month and year-end closing tasks; statutory reporting including VAT for UK entities; statutory audit for UK entities.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Brian Antoszyk</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Technical Accounting Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">USA, North Carolina</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Mashoura. Responsibilities: Advising on IFRS/IAS or GAAP matters; review of commercial contracts; supporting completion of Group Financial Statement.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Rudy Randuineau</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Intercompany Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">France</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Julia Rausch. Responsibilities: Managing intercompany process; preparing IC recharges, reconciliations, and Group calculations.</span>\n      </li>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Unai Muñoz</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Corporate Accountant</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Spain</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Julia Rausch. Responsibilities: Month and year-end closing tasks; statutory reporting for French, Spanish, and Danish entities; statutory audit for France, Spain, and Denmark.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Financial Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Sivakumar Govindan</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Manager, Financial Operations</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">India</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Bassem Masrouha. Responsibilities: Lead and manage team responsible for AP, Payments, AR, billing, and collections; primary point of contact for internal/external stakeholders; maintain KPIs.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">PMO</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Charlotta Hjalmarsson</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Director Financial Operations & Excellence</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">Sweden, Karlskrona</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Stefan Beitz. Responsibilities: Shift organization to process-driven environment; partner cross-functionally to identify gaps and improve efficiency via digital transformation and AI; ensure organization structure handles global complexity.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n\n  <section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n    <h3 itemprop=\"name\">Procurement</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li itemprop=\"employee\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Person\">\n        <strong itemprop=\"name\">Charlotte Friant</strong>\n        <span itemprop=\"jobTitle\">Senior Procurement Manager</span>\n        <span itemprop=\"workLocation\" itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Place\"><span itemprop=\"name\">The Netherlands, Amsterdam</span></span>\n        <span itemprop=\"description\">Manager: Thomas Bril. Responsibilities: Lead full sourcing lifecycle; perform commodity and supplier analysis; negotiate commercial terms; manage supplier lifecycle and risk; support supplier onboarding; assist with audits; primary Procurement POC for EWC, ENC, Broadcast, and PC&S; process improvement.</span>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n</section>",
                "Description": "<section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n  <h2 itemprop=\"name\">Finance Division</h2>\n  <p itemprop=\"description\">The Finance division at ESL FACEIT Group (EFG) is a global organization dedicated to maintaining financial integrity, supporting strategic decision-making, and ensuring regulatory compliance. Its purpose is to provide transparency, foster cross-departmental collaboration, and serve as a reliable point of contact for financial needs across the group. The division manages comprehensive financial planning, accounting, tax, treasury, and operational excellence to support EFG's business objectives.</p>\n\n  <h3>Core Pillars and Teams</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>FP&A and Controlling:</strong> Responsible for delivering 5-year plans, budgets, in-year re-forecasts, and monthly reporting. This pillar provides financial insights, profitability assessments, and business partnering for Esports and Digital units.</li>\n    <li><strong>Accounting, Tax & Treasury:</strong> Manages financial statement preparation, accounts payable/receivable, cash applications, and inventory accounting. This team ensures global legal and regulatory compliance, manages tax filings, transfer pricing, and oversees group liquidity and banking structures.</li>\n    <li><strong>Financial Operations & Excellence (PMO):</strong> Focuses on shifting the organization toward a process-driven environment, identifying gaps, and improving efficiency through digital transformation and AI.</li>\n    <li><strong>Financial Reporting:</strong> Manages group consolidation, statutory reporting, and ensures accuracy and compliance in financial statements for management and shareholders.</li>\n    <li><strong>Procurement:</strong> Leads the full sourcing lifecycle, manages supplier relationships, mitigates supply chain risks, and negotiates commercial terms to ensure cost-efficiency.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Resources</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/12OCuCqTuUsXUDVJ42ChU73Ykzr9qo78hZjS3kcZSwx8/edit?tab=t.0\">EFG Finance Team Documentation</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"https://eslfaceitgroup.lightning.force.com/lightning/page/home\">Sales Force</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
