                "Extra": "<section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/CreativeWork\">\n  <h2 itemprop=\"name\">Extra</h2>\n  <p itemprop=\"description\">Additional information regarding EFG Finance division operations, including prize money processes and service exceptions.</p>\n\n  <h3>Prize Money (Payment Labs)</h3>\n  <p>EFG has outsourced the service of paying out prize money for both B2C and B2B to Payment Labs Inc. All prize money related payments from 1 January 2026 and onwards are processed via this platform.</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Process Steps:</strong>\n      <ol>\n        <li>Set up the tournament on the platform by tournament operations.</li>\n        <li>Request the funding of the prize money by tournament operations.</li>\n        <li>Process the funding to the For Benefit Of (FBO) account on the platform by financial operations.</li>\n        <li>Request winners payment details set up the payments on the platform by tournament operations.</li>\n        <li>Collect and store the banking details from the winners on the platform by Payment Labs.</li>\n        <li>Submit the payment to the winners by the 'Payment Approval Group'.</li>\n        <li>Monthly reconciliation of the platform transactions and prize money payouts by financial operations.</li>\n      </ol>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Service Exceptions</h3>\n  <p>Certain services fall under specific accountability or control structures outside of standard procurement processes:</p>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Freelancers:</strong> Controlled by Division (selection based on professional expertise).</li>\n    <li><strong>Audit Companies:</strong> Controlled by ARC (appointed by the ARC directly).</li>\n    <li><strong>Legal Advisors:</strong> Controlled by Legal (per legal policy).</li>\n    <li><strong>Property Taxes & Public Charges:</strong> Controlled by Finance (unavoidable costs).</li>\n    <li><strong>Employee Benefits:</strong> Controlled by HR (e.g., health insurances).</li>\n    <li><strong>Governmental Service:</strong> Depends on service (mandatory due to local requirements, e.g., France Travail, Medical employee check).</li>\n    <li><strong>Banking services:</strong> Controlled by Finance (banking fees).</li>\n    <li><strong>Finance advisors:</strong> Controlled by Finance (under finance spend management).</li>\n    <li><strong>EOR / payroll services:</strong> Controlled by HR / US ops team (both FTE and freelancers).</li>\n    <li><strong>Advertisement Services:</strong> Controlled by Marketing (e.g., Tik Tok, Instagram, Google, Twitch).</li>\n    <li><strong>Players/Teams:</strong> Controlled by Esports (e.g., BootCamp, Team Merchandise).</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
